{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\ud83c\udf83 Welcome to <i>Spooky Night</i> \ud83c\udf83</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Trust is scarce, betrayal thrives, and every decision can be your last. <i>Spooky Night</i> is the ultimate  social deduction game, bringing friends and strangers together in a thrilling battle of wits and strategy. Will you expose the werewolves or fall victim to their cunning schemes? </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\ud83e\udde9 How to Play</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Day Phase</strong>: Talk with other players and vote to eliminate someone you think is a werewolf. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3443650/extras/chat.gif?t=1739383725\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>End of Day</strong>: The player with the most votes is eliminated and their role is revealed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3443650/extras/eliminate.gif?t=1739383725\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Night Phase</strong>: Werewolves attack, while villagers and other roles secretly use their abilities to protect, gather clues, or take action.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Win the Game</strong>:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Villagers win if all werewolves are eliminated.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Werewolves win if they equal or outnumber the villagers.</p></li></ul></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3443650/extras/intro.gif?t=1739383725\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\ud83c\udf89 Why You\u2019ll Love <i>Spooky Night</i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Every round is a fresh, unpredictable adventure. With a variety of unique roles and endless player strategies, no two games are ever the same. Build trust (or break it!).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This game is entirely free to play! You'll earn rewards after every match and can unlock a wide range of character customizations. Purchasing the game allows you to acquire skins faster and expand your inventory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3443650/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1739383725","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3443650/page.bg.jpg?t=1739383725","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3443650/84faf2037ba45ec2d7ebbf67b515dfb99cd506a3/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739383725","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3443650/84faf2037ba45ec2d7ebbf67b515dfb99cd506a3/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1739383725","categories":[{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"PvP","id":49},{"description":"Online PvP","id":36},{"description":"Co-op","id":9},{"description":"Online Co-op","id":38},{"description":"Cross-Platform Multiplayer","id":27}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\ud83c\udf83 Welcome to <i>Spooky Night</i> \ud83c\udf83</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Trust is scarce, betrayal thrives, and every decision can be your last. <i>Spooky Night</i> is the ultimate  social deduction game, bringing friends and strangers together in a thrilling battle of wits and strategy. Will you expose the werewolves or fall victim to their cunning schemes? </